title: Cheerleader U
overview: Follow the teammates of University of Kentucky's plucky Blue Squad as they cheer their way to the prestigious National College Cheerleading Championship over the course of eight grueling and emotional months. From tryouts to the finals in Orlando, Fla., these young athletes and coach Jomo Thompson and faculty adviser T. Lynn Williamson demonstrate the grit, sweat and determination of true champions in this absorbing six-episode series.
